OL,5,G1900 Alfred Hitchcock Presents
OL,6,     FThe Man with Two Faces: A talented
OL,7,     Fyoung actress seemingly destined
OL,8,     Ffor stardom appears to be under
OL,9,     Fthe spell of her unscrupulous and
OL,10,     Ftotally unprincipled husband. Mary
OL,11,     FAstor stars.
OL,12,G1930 Alfred Hitchcock Presents
OL,13,     FThe Changing Heart: Dane Ross is
OL,14,     Famazed by an old man's tales of
OL,15,     Fthe many clocks he's built - with
OL,16,     Fmoving parts, marching soldiers
OL,17,     Fand flying birds - and is asked to
OL,18,     Fstay for dinner.
